headline: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) Reports Strong Q2 Earnings with US$1.31 Billion Revenue
summary: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) recently announced its second quarter results for 2025, reporting a robust improvement in financial performance, with sales increasing to $1,306 million and net income doubling year-over-year. These strong figures likely supported the company's impressive 20% share price increase over the past month. Additionally, Keysight's collaboration with major industry players such as Fujitsu and Intel, along with new product launches and a positive outlook for the next...
